title: Youtube recorded rank climb with a possible team, get in early and it might go somewhere?!?!?!
body:
Just gonna record my games, and whoever wants to join can, just have to be a semi decent player with a preferred lane. Any elo is fine, as I'm in bronze 3 and plan on going ham with climbing. So hit me up, and maybe we can make a name of ourselves. :)

IGN: MyDadsDumbFace
ELO: Bronze 3 (23LP)
LANE: Top/jg
CHAMPION/CHAMPION TYPE: Renekton/Tryndamere|Bruisers/Off-tanks
USUAL ONLINE TIME: 9AM-7PM Anywhere between there. (Adelaide time)
[](http://24timezones.com/world_directory/time_in_adelaide.php)

I hope to see a few players hit me up. :) 
GLHF

replies.body:
You should record your games, and then re-watch it.
Learn how you could have avoided ganks, roamed, ganked etc.

By re-watching your games you should improve, as long as you accept that you messed up on occasions.
This looks very interesting, I am a bronze 2 player who is looking to improve my own gameplay knowledge and awareness, my preferred role can be anything so add me if it sparks your interest XD
im interested, can fill any lane, feel free to add me. online between 4pm-10pm sydney time all week, all day weekends
I'm always looking for people to duo with so send me a friend request if you want.  I usually play adc and mid.
